items.content: Some of the data I collected is from the NMS wiki homepage. If you want to know more about this topic, please visit https://nomanssky.gamepedia.com/Multi-tool_Catalogue

The first thing you should know is that there are 4 different types of multi tools: pistol, rifle, experimental and alien. Every multi tool can have a rank from "S" to "C" Each of them  have different specializations.

Every time you start a new game, you will spawn with    a multi tool pistol typed. That means you start the game with a mining boost.
You can buy multi tools in space stations
The pistol typed multi tools could have following ranks and stats.

Rifle typed multi tools have a big advantage in damage .
They are the best choice for you if you like to destroy guards.
You can buy multi tools in space stations.

They can scan faster than the other multi tool types.
The best choice for explorers.
You can buy multi tools in space stations.

The alien type is the alrounder of the multi tool industry.
They have a minig boost, damage boost and scanning boost.
All in one.
